\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/b_WdkLkJiIk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fb_WdkLkJiIk&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixYoeW3mBCvqo%2FKk1k%2BmNMw8%3D&h=fefb0018\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/b_WdkLkJiIk</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:46:18.000Z","msg":"慶狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87c3030f159b2c49af34e149e6c802266977e02f","tid":2449970,"uid":301952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:46:50.000Z","msg":"懷疑江華戴假髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef90010f06db71f5ad26d0db77f4903af29b5b4b","tid":2449970,"uid":62850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:48:08.000Z","msg":"因為佢太有自信啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8536a42b3854a84ee2627c34ad69809eb1de1fbe","tid":2449970,"uid":241449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:50:04.000Z","msg":"佢唔係去賣保險咩....<br />\n其實當年見佢笑鳩阿舜已經覺得咩料你自己好撚叻咩"},{"pid":"b8b8598d1b9d1b3595dc82065196c6d3f9c6042e","tid":2449970,"uid":32128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8536a42b3854a84ee2627c34ad69809eb1de1fbe","tid":2449970,"uid":241449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T07:50:04.000Z","msg":"佢唔係去賣保險咩....<br />\n其實當年見佢笑鳩阿舜已經覺得咩料你自己好撚叻咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:10:53.000Z","msg":"連登仔做評判一定屌到阿舜成隻狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a978d47ffa2deebda5370f95953797c3f04af2","tid":2449970,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8b8598d1b9d1b3595dc82065196c6d3f9c6042e","tid":2449970,"uid":32128,